<ItacWorkItem RecordId="023-000003701" WorkId="000493"><ShortTitle>Dialogi Maritimi di M. Gioan Iacopo Bottazzo</ShortTitle><LongTitle>Et alcune rime maritime di M. Nicolo Franco, et d`altri diversi spiriti, dell`Accademia degli Argonauti.
All`Eccellenza del Machese di Soncino, Il S. Conte Massimiano Stampa.</LongTitle><ItacAcademyItem AcademyId="0477" RecordID="021-000007906">Accademia degli Argonauti (Casale Monferrato)</ItacAcademyItem><Format>8&#186;</Format><City CityId="67"><PublicationPlaceItalianName>Mantova</PublicationPlaceItalianName><PublicationPlaceEnglishName>Mantua</PublicationPlaceEnglishName><PublicationPlaceLatinName>Mantua</PublicationPlaceLatinName></City><PublicationYear>1547</PublicationYear><DedicationPlaceDate>Casale Monferrato</DedicationPlaceDate><Shelfmark>12350.b.20. |239.b.15.</Shelfmark><Content>The first part is by Gioan Iacopo Bottazzo and is divided into three parts, each part in the form of a dialogue discussing a different theme. The themes are geography, the winds and the celestial world. The second part is comprised of the Rime of Nicolo Franco and other members of the Argonauti.</Content><Subjects>Geography|Geology|Meteorology|Chemistry|Poetry|Love|Astronomy|Natural Philosophy|Philosophy|Natural History</Subjects><Language>Italian</Language><Pagination>pp. 168</Pagination><Marginalia>No</Marginalia><Authors><ItacPersonItem PersonId="9128" RecordID="022-000001735">Bottazzo,Gioan Iacopo,,Early 16th C.-?</ItacPersonItem></Authors><Contributors><ItacPersonItem PersonId="9113" RecordID="022-000001720">Franco,Nicolo,,1515-1570</ItacPersonItem><ItacPersonItem PersonId="9262" RecordID="022-000001550">Pico,Cristoforo,,late 16th C.-17th C.</ItacPersonItem><ItacPersonItem PersonId="9013" RecordID="022-000001581">Catalano,Pietro,,16th C.</ItacPersonItem><ItacPersonItem PersonId="9149" RecordID="022-000001599">Del Pero,Giovan Jacopo,,16th C.</ItacPersonItem><ItacPersonItem PersonId="9139" RecordID="022-000001620">De` Malvezzi,Bessario,,16th C.</ItacPersonItem><ItacPersonItem PersonId="9035" RecordID="022-000001625">Montiglio,Giovan Francesco,,16th C.</ItacPersonItem><ItacPersonItem PersonId="9057" RecordID="022-000001647">Giustiniano,Girolamo,,ca. 1560-?</ItacPersonItem><ItacP